## NAMING CONVENTIONS

| Thing | Convention | Example |
|---|---|---|
| Python files | `snake_case` | `ai_service.py` |
| Classes | `PascalCase` | `DarkPatternDetector` |
| Functions / methods | `snake_case` | `compute_score()` |
| Constants | `UPPER_SNAKE` | `SCORE_MAP` |
| Type aliases | `PascalCase` | `type FindingList = list[Finding]` |
| JS functions | `camelCase` | `renderOverlay()` |
| CSS classes | `kebab-case` with `clarity-` prefix | `.clarity-overlay` |

